    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Recitallion</strong> takes the basic gameplay loop of card games and adds a good dose of heart-pounding action  for a hectic and strategic competitive witch-themed experience. On top of playing your cards' two effects strategically, player must also position themselves to dodge and strike back effectively! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/a0f0ea832a826ce7b91192232a0b1973.avif?t=1738349327\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras_big/a0f0ea832a826ce7b91192232a0b1973.avif?t=1738349327 width=800 height=103 /></span><strong>A Battle of Wits and Reflexes:</strong> Strategize around the grid and balance between ruining your opponent's life and making yours easier. But do it fast, because everything happens in real time and at high speed. Think fast, and act faster. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/7f1347845f4258895a516ac6539e5110.poster.avif?t=1738349327\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/7f1347845f4258895a516ac6539e5110.webm?t=1738349327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/7f1347845f4258895a516ac6539e5110.mp4?t=1738349327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/c51a2db22f61141224f45d36cea7451d.avif?t=1738349327\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras_big/c51a2db22f61141224f45d36cea7451d.avif?t=1738349327 width=800 height=103 /></span><strong>Carve YOUR Path to Victory:</strong> From personalizing your decks, to smart summon placement to playing cards in your mode of choice, there are many variables in Recitallion that let you find your own way of winning.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/e586b882da0b30bbcbdb8fdca627e421.poster.avif?t=1738349327\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/e586b882da0b30bbcbdb8fdca627e421.webm?t=1738349327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/e586b882da0b30bbcbdb8fdca627e421.mp4?t=1738349327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/396460c9a1d38d63fb702e3e782b477b.avif?t=1738349327\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras_big/396460c9a1d38d63fb702e3e782b477b.avif?t=1738349327 width=800 height=103 /></span><strong>Manage your Deck, Manage your Life: </strong>Your deck of cards is very limited, and if you end up out of cards, your hp will start draining. To help manage this deck is Summon Theft: by destroying an opponent’s summon, you can get the corresponding card added to your deck.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/9100a3c44082e08094582fe60479e1db.poster.avif?t=1738349327\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/9100a3c44082e08094582fe60479e1db.webm?t=1738349327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323310/extras/9100a3c44082e08094582fe60479e1db.mp4?t=1738349327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
